changelog.comment: New entry. Added TalE as auxiliary enzyme (phosphorylation step is required for glycosylation); corrected "installation of dTDP-L-rhamnose" to "installation of L-rhamnose", since only the sugar moiety is retained, while the dTDP is cleaved off.

reactions.description: Glycosylation of phosphoramidon peptidic intermediate with L-rhamnose
Installation of L-rhamnose on the phosphoramidon peptidic intermediate, leading to phosphoramidon
